{"tid":1097033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果未放棄 iPhone SE 系列，預計新款將於第 3 季更名上市","createTime":"2019-04-08T06:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T14:44:16.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f212ab5cd896356447cb2d298a1b123fc05e57b8","tid":1097033,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:32:32.000Z","msg":"蘋果未放棄 iPhone SE 系列，預計新款將於第 3 季更名上市<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/04/08/apple-iphone-xe/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F04%2F08%2Fapple-iphone-xe%2F&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfp6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=0dc00d6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/04/08/apple-iphone-xe/</a><br />\n<br />\n日前，在蘋果的春季發表會中，市場原本預計蘋果可能會發表旗下螢幕最小的 iPhone SE 改良版 iPhone SE 2，不過，最終仍讓大家失望了。而如今，根據國外媒體《PC-Tablet》的報導，蘋果仍將會發表 iPhone SE 改良版的改良版，只是名稱可能會改變，而且最快將會在 2019 年的第 3 季正式問世。<br />\n<br />\n因為目前競爭對手的產品，越來越朝向大螢幕的方向發展，因此使得蘋果的 iPhone 也不得不跟隨潮流，使得僅有 4.7 吋螢幕的 iPhone SE 越來越不吃香。所以，之前有市場傳言，蘋果最終將放棄 iPhone SE 的後續發展。不過，根據《PC-Tablet》的報導，他們自印度富士康內部所得到的消息顯示，目前蘋果並沒有準備放棄 iPhone SE 系列，而且還將採用新的命名方式，使得新一代的 iPhone SE 改名為 iPhone XE。<br />\n<br />\n報導進一步指出，新的 iPhone XE 可能將採用 4.8 吋的 AMOLED 螢幕，並且取消實體按鍵，支援 Face ID 解鎖功能，而且預計將搭載最新的 A12 處理器，使其運算功能強大。至於，在許多人所關心的攝影功能方面，iPhone XE 的後置鏡頭預計將搭載一顆 f/1.8、具備 1,200 萬像素的單攝攝影鏡頭，這將與當前的 iPhone XR 配備相類似。<br />\n<br />\n最後，在售價方面，新的 iPhone XE 預計將會從 600 美元起跳（約新台幣 18,600 元），而高大儲存容量版本的 iPhone XE，售價則將近 800 美元（約新台幣 24,860 元）。新的 iPhone XE，則是預計將會在 2019 年的第 3 季推出。而在手機逐漸走向大螢幕、高螢幕占比的趨勢下，新一代小螢幕的 iPhone XE 是否能受到市場的青睞，就有待市場的反應而定了。"},{"pid":"131b5da79232c1b2da75f9213b6e9fe6b48eafc3","tid":1097033,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7450e94649813135d49ab7e1c217b19df072d46","tid":1097033,"uid":208689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2189326a64995e86891d46a6b2381d615a7dbb3","tid":1097033,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:37:30.000Z","msg":"依家做咩都慢半拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9877e12f8fcb8fb47d3d79de944e78f032574f7a","tid":1097033,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:39:07.000Z","msg":"「預計」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458da73597231ceba79a91cfe85b4bf016d1032f","tid":1097033,"uid":124320,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:39:45.000Z","msg":"究竟係傳媒未放棄定apple未放棄?"},{"pid":"fd4a695f8510fde3130f670244f0564e6aff4116","tid":1097033,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:40:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2a8b8378876897e2b46019843e3a82ed596892c","tid":1097033,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本7已經係用黎取代se"},{"pid":"9a83e6a81989b869b021da5f8fdf81a7883cd4d6","tid":1097033,"uid":51532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:46:28.000Z","msg":"4.7 吋螢幕的 iPhone SE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e11bb5655c1453d414f923f32add110d8f1249a","tid":1097033,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"IPHONE全球市佔率越黎越低"},{"pid":"b97e31b4d96dc2e8aeec476a7dd0470ea5aabfe5","tid":1097033,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":